---
import { User, Phone, MessageSquare, ChevronDown, Building2, Mail, Send } from 'lucide-astro';

---
<section id="contacto" class="bg-white py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto"><div class="text-center mb-16"><p class="text-[#78BE20] text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-3">Solicita tu propuesta personalizada</p><h2 class="text-[#0F2E65] text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3">Contáctenos</h2><p class="text-gray-500 text-base max-w-md mx-auto">Cuéntanos de tu empresa y te contactamos en menos de 24 horas.</p><div class="w-16 h-1 bg-[#78BE20] mx-auto mt-6 rounded-full"></div></div><div class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12 items-start"><div class="lg:col-span-2 flex justify-center lg:justify-start"><div class="relative"><div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-[#0F2E65]/5 rounded-[2rem] -rotate-3"></div><div class="relative bg-[#F8FAFC] rounded-2xl p-2 shadow-sm"><img alt="Professional consultant" class="w-full max-w-sm rounded-xl object-contain" src="/assets/asset_2.jpg"><div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 shadow-lg border border-gray-100"><p class="text-[#0F2E65] text-sm font-semibold">Respuesta garantizada</p><p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mt-0.5">En menos de 24 horas hábiles</p></div></div></div></div><form class="lg:col-span-3 space-y-6"><div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5"><div class="space-y-2"><label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#0F2E65] text-sm font-semibold"><User class="lucide lucide-user w-4 h-4 text-[#78BE20]" />Nombre completo</label><input required="" placeholder="Tu nombre" class="w-full bg-[#F8FAFC] border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-gray-800 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#78BE20]/30 focus:border-[#78BE20] transition-all duration-200 placeholder:text-gray-400" type="text" value="" name="nombre"></div><div class="space-y-2"><label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#0F2E65] text-sm font-semibold"><Phone class="lucide lucide-phone w-4 h-4 text-[#78BE20]" />Teléfono</label><input required="" placeholder="10 dígitos" class="w-full bg-[#F8FAFC] border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-gray-800 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#78BE20]/30 focus:border-[#78BE20] transition-all duration-200 placeholder:text-gray-400" type="tel" value="" name="telefono"></div></div><div class="space-y-2"><label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#0F2E65] text-sm font-semibold"><MessageSquare class="lucide lucide-message-square w-4 h-4 text-[#78BE20]" />¿Qué necesitas?</label><div class="relative"><select name="necesidad" class="w-full bg-[#F8FAFC] border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-gray-800 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#78BE20]/30 focus:border-[#78BE20] transition-all duration-200 placeholder:text-gray-400 appearance-none cursor-pointer pr-10"><option value="">Selecciona una opción</option><option value="conectividad">Conectividad</option><option value="seguridad">Seguridad</option><option value="otro">Otro</option></select><ChevronDown class="lucide lucide-chevron-down absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 pointer-events-none" /></div></div><div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5"><div class="space-y-2"><label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#0F2E65] text-sm font-semibold"><Building2 class="lucide lucide-building2 lucide-building-2 w-4 h-4 text-[#78BE20]" />Compañía / Giro</label><input required="" placeholder="Nombre de tu empresa" class="w-full bg-[#F8FAFC] border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-gray-800 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#78BE20]/30 focus:border-[#78BE20] transition-all duration-200 placeholder:text-gray-400" type="text" value="" name="compania"></div><div class="space-y-2"><label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#0F2E65] text-sm font-semibold"><Mail class="lucide lucide-mail w-4 h-4 text-[#78BE20]" />Email</label><input required="" placeholder="tu@email.com" class="w-full bg-[#F8FAFC] border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-gray-800 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#78BE20]/30 focus:border-[#78BE20] transition-all duration-200 placeholder:text-gray-400" type="email" value="" name="email"></div></div><div class="space-y-2"><label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#0F2E65] text-sm font-semibold"><MessageSquare class="lucide lucide-message-square w-4 h-4 text-[#78BE20]" />Mensaje</label><textarea name="mensaje" rows="3" placeholder="Cuéntanos brevemente qué necesitas..." class="w-full bg-[#F8FAFC] border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-gray-800 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#78BE20]/30 focus:border-[#78BE20] transition-all duration-200 placeholder:text-gray-400 resize-none"></textarea></div><div class="pt-2"><button type="submit" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-[#0F2E65] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-[#0a1f45] hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-[#0F2E65]/20 transition-all duration-300">Enviar y recibir propuesta<Send class="lucide lucide-send w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" /></button></div><p class="text-gray-400 text-xs">Tu información está protegida. No compartimos datos con terceros.</p></form></div></div></section>
